headline.print_headline: Somali President, Prime Minister Spar Over Cabinet Reshuffle
headline.main: Somali President, Prime Minister Spar Over Cabinet Reshuffle

lead_paragraph: Somalia's president has instructed his cabinet to ignore a cabinet reshuffle by the prime minister, highlighting a possible rift at a time when Somalia is looking to build confidence in its government and reassure donors.
